## FEATURE-SPECIFIC PROMPTS

### Prompt 1: Image Generator

```
StwÃ³rz React komponent "ImageGenerator" z nastÄ™pujÄ…cymi wymaganiami:

FUNKCJONALNOÅšÄ†:
1. Text input dla prompt
2. Model selector (Flux Pro, DALL-E 3, Stable Diffusion)
3. Style presets (Professional, Creative, Photorealistic, Animated)
4. Aspect ratio selector (Square, Portrait, Landscape, Custom)
5. Advanced options (steps, guidance, seed)

UI/UX:
- Input field z sugestiami z AI (hint text)
- Loading state z animacjÄ…
- Generated image display z zoom/pan
- Quick actions: Download, Copy URL, Share, Add to favorites
- Gallery view wszystkich generacji
- History list z thumbnails

BACKEND:
1. POST /api/v1/generation/text-to-image
   - Input: prompt, model, aspectRatio, options
   - Output: imageUrl, id, metadata
   
2. Fallback logic:
   - Try Flux Pro
   - If fails, try DALL-E 3
   - If fails, try Stable Diffusion
   - If all fail, return error

INTEGRACJE:
- Replicate API dla Flux
- OpenAI API dla DALL-E
- Stability AI API dla SD
- Error handling i retries

STORAGE:
- Save to database
- Cache thumbnails
- Keep history

Kod musi byÄ‡:
- Production-ready
- Fully typed (TypeScript)
- With error handling
- With loading states
- With accessibility features
- Mobile responsive
- With proper styling (Tailwind)
```

### Prompt 2: Chatbot

```
StwÃ³rz React hook "useChat" do komunikacji z AI chatbotem.

WYMAGANIA:
1. Real-time streaming responses
