3. DELETE /api/v1/chat/conversations/{id} - Delete
4. POST /api/v1/chat/conversations/{id}/export - Export

AI CONFIGURATION:
- Model: Gemini 2.0 Flash
- System prompts dla kaÅ¼dej roli
- Streaming enabled
- Temperature: 0.7
- Max tokens: 2048

WEBSOCKET:
- Real-time message delivery
- Presence indicators
- Typing indicators (optional)

Code must be:
- Hook pattern
- Custom hooks for state
- Error boundaries
- Retry logic
- Proper TypeScript
```

